title: Magic Tracer 2.0.010 with crack
description:
MagicTracer is a raster to vector converter for Windows. With over 100 customizable functions, MagicTracer works as your all-purpose tool for raster to vector converting. It even comes complete with a simple interface and real-time previews that allow you to see how a custom setting will affect your project.

   *  Support for image scanners
   * Support for raster image formats: PSD, BMP, GIF, JPG, TIF, TGA, PCX, etc.
   * Includes both raster and vector editing tools
   * Vector conversion settings for different types of images
   * Exports to DXF for editing in CAD and Vector programs
   * Additional support for exporting EPS, EMF, WMF, SVG, DC2, XYZ
   * Allows custom user-specified sizes for vector output
   * Real-time previews for both raster and vector editing
   * Step-by-step tutorials and documentation of the commands are included
